sections.heading: Officers; entry and inspection authorized
sections.text: Any officer authorized to enforce the Game Law may, at any time, enter an aquaculture facility for the purpose of inspecting the facility or for the purpose of enforcing the Game Law.SourceLaws 1929, c. 112, VII, ยง 11, p. 441;C.S.1929, ยง 37-711;R.S.1943, ยง 3
